---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Gann Astrofinancial Panel · XAUUSD Astro Database — Dashboard Terpadu" description="Peta korespondensi planet-komoditas-zodiak, siklus aspek, kalkulator Square of 9, Jam Planet Kaldean, dan database harian efemeris + harga OHLC XAUUSD 10 tahun.">
  <Header />

  <div class="xauusd-terpadu-page">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&family=Spectral:wght@400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <div class="stars"></div>

    <div class="maintabs">
      <button class="tabbtn active" data-tab="gann">Gann Astrofinancial Panel</button>
      <button class="tabbtn" data-tab="database">XAUUSD Astro Database</button>
    </div>

    <div id="tab-gann" class="tabpanel active">
      <header>
        <div class="eyebrow">Astro · Numero · Price</div>
        <h1>Gann Astrofinancial Panel</h1>
        <p>Peta korespondensi planet–komoditas–zodiak–house, siklus aspek, deklinasi, gerhana, dan kalkulator Square of 9 — disusun mengikuti kerangka WD Gann.</p>
      </header>

      <main>
        <section id="executive-summary">
          <div class="section-head"><span class="num">00</span><h2>Executive Summary &amp; Master Signal Table</h2><span class="sub">SEMUA SIGNAL, 1 TEMPAT</span></div>

          <div class="card" style="border-color:var(--gold)">
            <h3>Ringkasan Eksekutif</h3>
            <p>Dashboard ini menguji <b>60+ signal astrofinansial</b> terhadap XAUUSD pakai data asli 50 tahun (1975-2025, 13.115 hari). Temuan utama:</p>
            <p style="margin-top:8px">1. <b>Winter Solstice (21 Des) = signal paling reliable lintas-kalender</b> — 63% win-rate, konsisten juga di dashboard IHSG (90%).<br>
            2. <b>Syawwal &amp; Ramadhan = 2 bulan Hijriah terkuat</b> (69% &amp; 62%) — 5 dari 6 perang besar Islam terjadi di 2 bulan ini.<br>
            3. <b>Juli &amp; Januari = 2 bulan Masehi terkuat</b> (65% &amp; 61%) — overlap sama Sun→Leo ingress &amp; January effect.<br>
            4. <b>Peristiwa geopolitik/perang (bukan bencana alam) paling konsisten dorong Gold naik</b> — 70% dari 10 krisis dunia yang diuji.<br>
            5. <b>Sampel kecil bisa menyesatkan</b> — Venus-Jupiter Conjunction awalnya keliatan 75% bullish (4 sampel), ternyata cuma 52% setelah diperluas ke 54 kejadian.</p>
          </div>

          <h3 style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:19px;color:var(--gold);margin:20px 0 10px">Grafik: Top 15 Signal Terkuat</h3>
          <div class="table-wrap" style="padding:16px;background:var(--panel)">
            <svg id="masterChart" viewBox="0 0 700 420" width="100%" style="max-width:700px;display:block;margin:0 auto"></svg>
          </div>

          <h3 style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:19px;color:var(--gold);margin:24px 0 10px">Master Signal Table</h3>
          <div class="toolbar" style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px">
            <input id="signalSearch" placeholder="cari signal (misal: Leo, Ramadhan, Solstice)..." style="flex:1;min-width:220px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:9px 12px;border-radius:6px">
          </div>
          <div class="toolbar" style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px" id="filterButtons">
            <button class="filter-btn active" data-cat="all">Semua</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Ingress">Ingress</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Aspek">Aspek</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Lunar">Lunar</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Kalender Gann">Kalender Gann</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Hijriah">Hijriah</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Masehi">Masehi</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Sejarah">Sejarah</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Bullish">Bullish (&gt;55%)</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-cat="Bearish">Bearish (&lt;45%)</button>
          </div>
          <div class="table-wrap">
            <table>
              <thead><tr><th>Signal</th><th>Kategori</th><th>Win Rate</th><th>Score</th><th>n</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody id="masterSignalBody"></tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px"><h3>#6 — Apakah Semua Udah Di-Backtest?</h3><p><b>Yang UDAH di-backtest data asli (real price):</b> semua ingress (Sun/Venus/Mars/Jupiter/Saturn), semua aspek (Jupiter-Saturn, Mars-Saturn, Sun-Jupiter, Mars-Jupiter, Venus-Jupiter, +5 aspek tambahan), Full/New Moon, 8 hari Gann, 12 bulan Hijriah, 12 bulan Masehi, tanggal-tanggal penting Islam (berulang), dan peristiwa dunia 1976-2025.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:8px"><b>Yang BELUM/TIDAK BISA di-backtest (cuma astro simbolis):</b> Sirah Nabawiyah asli (571-632 M — Gold belum ada), peristiwa dunia sebelum 1975 (VOC 1602, Bretton Woods 1944, dll — di luar data floating-price). Yang ini ditandain jelas di section masing-masing dengan label "ASTRO MURNI, TANPA DATA HARGA".</p>
          <p style="margin-top:8px"><b>Belum ada:</b> data 20 tahun-lebih-baru buat konfirmasi ulang beberapa temuan awal (misal window Jupiter-Saturn Opposition idealnya butuh 2-3x siklus 20 tahun buat sampel lebih besar dari n=94 sekarang).</p></div>
        </section>

        <section id="table">
          <div class="section-head"><span class="num">01</span><h2>Tabel Korespondensi Planet</h2><span class="sub">DATA TABLE</span></div>
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>Planet</th><th>Komoditas / Aset</th><th>Zodiak Natural</th><th>House</th><th>Peran di Pasar</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">☉</span>Matahari (Sun)</td><td><span class="tag gold">Emas (Gold)</span></td><td>Leo</td><td>5 — Spekulasi</td><td>Nilai inti, tren utama, ego pasar / bull leadership</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">☽</span>Bulan (Moon)</td><td><span class="tag silver">Perak (Silver)</span></td><td>Cancer</td><td>4 — Domestik</td><td>Volatilitas harian, siklus pasang-surut harga, stabilitas pasar domestik</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">☿</span>Merkurius (Mercury)</td><td>Berita / Saham Retail / Transportasi</td><td>Gemini · Virgo</td><td>3 — Komunikasi</td><td>Arus berita, sentimen retail, retrograde = simpang siur &amp; panik jangka pendek</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">♀</span>Venus</td><td>Currency (FX) / Tembaga / Barang mewah</td><td>Taurus · Libra</td><td>2 · 7 — Nilai &amp; Kemitraan</td><td>Nilai tukar, daya beli, harmoni/ketidakseimbangan neraca dagang</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">♂</span>Mars</td><td><span class="tag mars">Minyak Bumi (Oil) / Energi</span></td><td>Aries · Scorpio</td><td>1 — Aksi</td><td>Agresi, perang, lonjakan energi, entri impulsif</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">♃</span>Jupiter</td><td>Indeks Saham / Ekspansi Kredit</td><td>Sagittarius · Pisces</td><td>9 — Ekspansi</td><td>Optimisme, siklus bull besar, inflasi kredit</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">♄</span>Saturn</td><td>Timbal / Komoditas Struktural / Deflasi</td><td>Capricorn · Aquarius</td><td>10 — Struktur</td><td>Pembatasan, resesi, siklus makro jangka panjang</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">♅</span>Uranus</td><td>Saham Teknologi / Kripto</td><td>Aquarius</td><td>11 — Disrupsi</td><td>Kejutan mendadak, gap, crash/rally tiba-tiba</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">♆</span>Neptune</td><td><span class="tag mars">Minyak Bumi (Oil) — co-ruler</span></td><td>Pisces</td><td>12 — Tersembunyi</td><td>Ilusi, manipulasi data cadangan, minyak = cairan tersembunyi di bawah tanah</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="planet-sym">♇</span>Pluto</td><td>Tambang Dalam / Uranium / Restrukturisasi Utang</td><td>Scorpio</td><td>8 — Sumber Daya Bersama</td><td>Transformasi besar, krisis utang, reset struktural</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </section>

        <section id="oil-mercury">
          <div class="section-head"><span class="num">02</span><h2>Fokus: Berita/Mercury &amp; Entitas Minyak</h2></div>
          <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
              <h3>☿ Mercury → Berita &amp; Retail</h3>
              <p>Mercury menguasai arus informasi, media, dan saham ritel/transportasi. Kondisi normal = berita mengalir jelas &amp; terpola.</p>
              <div class="rule">Retrograde: berita jadi simpang siur, rumor mendominasi, saham retail rawan panik jual jangka pendek. Reversal palsu meningkat — kurangi ukuran posisi selama window retrograde.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3>☽ Moon → Silver</h3>
              <p>Cancer, House 4. Mengatur volatilitas harian (siklus lunar ~29.5 hari), pasang-surut harga jangka pendek, dan stabilitas pasar domestik.</p>
              <div class="rule">New Moon / Full Moon sering jadi titik micro-turn intraday-swing pada Silver &amp; XAUUSD.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3>♂ / ♆ Entitas Minyak Bumi</h3>
              <p>Oil dikuasai ganda: Mars (energi, agresi geopolitik) dan Neptune (cairan tersembunyi, ketidakpastian data OPEC/cadangan). Zodiak natural: Scorpio–Pisces.</p>
              <div class="rule">Neptune bertemu Mars (konjungsi/aspek keras) → lonjakan atau volatilitas ekstrem pada harga minyak.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="aspects">
          <div class="section-head"><span class="num">03</span><h2>Siklus Aspek &amp; Transit</h2></div>
          <div class="cards">
            <div class="card"><h3>Aspek Genap (90° / 120° / 180°)</h3><p>Sudut keras (square 90°, oposisi 180°) memicu volatilitas/pembalikan; sudut trine 120° cenderung memuluskan tren.</p>
              <div class="rule">Neptune–Mars square/konjungsi → lonjakan volatilitas ekstrem di Oil.</div></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Mercury Retrograde</h3><p>Transit mundur semu Mercury.</p>
              <div class="rule">Berita simpang siur → panik jangka pendek di saham retail. Hindari breakout trading murni saat retrograde.</div></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Jupiter–Saturn (~20 Tahun)</h3><p>Grand Mutation — siklus makro ekonomi terbesar Gann.</p>
              <div class="rule">Menentukan arah inflasi/deflasi jangka panjang &amp; siklus komoditas energi (Oil, Batu Bara).</div></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Mars–Saturn (~2 Tahun)</h3><p>Friksi agresi vs struktur.</p>
              <div class="rule">Sering memicu crash/panik geopolitik → Gold melonjak sebagai safe haven.</div></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Extreme Declination</h3><p>Planet mencapai Maximum North/South.</p>
              <div class="rule">Komoditas yang dikuasainya cenderung membentuk Major High/Low mutlak.</div></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Parallel &amp; Kontra-Parallel</h3><p>Dua planet berdeklinasi sama.</p>
              <div class="rule">Efek setara konjungsi 0° — perkuat sinyal turning point saat berbarengan dengan level SQ9.</div></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Gerhana di Zodiak Natural</h3><p>Eclipse tepat di derajat zodiak komoditas (Leo=Gold, Pisces=Oil).</p>
              <div class="rule">Bertindak sebagai Time Turn — window pembalikan agresif: −3 hari s/d +3 hari dari gerhana.</div></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="ingress-history">
          <div class="section-head"><span class="num">04</span><h2>History Ingress Jupiter/Saturn vs Gold — 50 Tahun</h2><span class="sub">DATA ASLI · GCUSD · 1975-2025</span></div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-dim);margin:-6px 0 14px">
            Semua kejadian ingress domisili Jupiter/Saturn yang kedeteksi dalam 50 tahun terakhir (data floating-price penuh sejak akhir Bretton Woods). Window: 5 hari sebelum vs 14 hari sesudah.
          </p>
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>Tanggal Ingress</th><th>Planet → Zodiak</th><th>Harga Sblm</th><th>Harga Stlh</th><th>Perubahan</th><th>Sentimen</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>25 Des 1982</td><td><span class="tag gold">Jupiter → Sagittarius (domisili)</span></td><td>446,9</td><td>483,2</td><td style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:700">+8,1% ⬆⬆</td><td style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:700">Bullish Kuat</td></tr>
              <tr><td>12 Feb 1988</td><td><span class="tag">Saturn → Capricorn (domisili)</span></td><td>443,2</td><td>431,1</td><td>−2,7% ⬇</td><td>Bearish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>11 Nov 1988</td><td><span class="tag">Saturn → Capricorn (re-entry)</span></td><td>423,5</td><td>423,3</td><td>−0,0% (flat)</td><td>Netral/Flat</td></tr>
              <tr><td>6 Feb 1991</td><td><span class="tag">Saturn → Aquarius (domisili)</span></td><td>368,7</td><td>366,1</td><td>−0,7% ⬇</td><td>Bearish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>3 Jul 1993</td><td><span class="tag">Saturn → Aquarius (re-entry)</span></td><td>376,1</td><td>392,4</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+4,3% ⬆</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">Bullish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>9 Des 1994</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Sagittarius (domisili)</span></td><td>379,0</td><td>382,3</td><td>+0,9% ⬆</td><td>Bullish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>20 Feb 1986</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Pisces (domisili)</span></td><td>336,2</td><td>344,3</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+2,4% ⬆</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">Bullish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>5 Feb 1998</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Pisces (re-entry)</span></td><td>304,6</td><td>300,4</td><td>−1,4% ⬇</td><td>Bearish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>19 Jan 2010</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Pisces (domisili)</span></td><td>1.143,0</td><td>1.118,0</td><td>−2,2% ⬇</td><td>Bearish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>8 Sep 2010</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Pisces (re-entry)</span></td><td>1.251,1</td><td>1.292,1</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+3,3% ⬆</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">Bullish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>23 Des 2017</td><td><span class="tag">Saturn → Capricorn (domisili)</span></td><td>1.246,0</td><td>1.309,0</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+4,3% ⬆</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">Bullish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>10 Nov 2018</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Sagittarius (domisili)</span></td><td>1.232,3</td><td>1.222,4</td><td>−0,8% ⬇ flat</td><td>Netral/Flat</td></tr>
              <tr><td>26 Mar 2020</td><td><span class="tag gold">Saturn → Aquarius (COVID crash)</span></td><td>1.484,6</td><td>1.752,8</td><td style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:700">+18,1% ⬆⬆ major low</td><td style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:700">Bullish Ekstrem</td></tr>
              <tr><td>28 Jun 2020</td><td><span class="tag">Saturn → Capricorn (re-entry)</span></td><td>1.782,0</td><td>1.814,1</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+1,8% ⬆</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">Bullish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>20 Des 2020</td><td><span class="tag gold">Saturn → Aquarius (Great Conjunction)</span></td><td>1.855,3</td><td>1.946,6</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+4,9% ⬆</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">Bullish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>17 Mei 2021</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Pisces (domisili)</span></td><td>1.822,8</td><td>1.905,0</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+4,5% ⬆</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">Bullish</td></tr>
              <tr><td>31 Des 2021</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Pisces (re-entry)</span></td><td>1.811,7</td><td>1.816,5</td><td>+0,3% (flat)</td><td>Netral/Flat</td></tr>
              <tr><td>25 Okt 2022</td><td><span class="tag">Jupiter → Pisces (re-entry)</span></td><td>1.636,8</td><td>1.716,0</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+4,8% ⬆</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">Bullish</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px">
            <h3>Temuan (17 kejadian, 50 tahun)</h3>
            <p><b>12 dari 17 ingress → Gold naik (71%).</b> Saturn→Aquarius (gabungan): 3/4 naik, avg +6,7% — termasuk +18,1% di Mar 2020 (COVID crash, major low). Saturn→Capricorn: 2/4 naik (50%, lebih lemah dari kesan window 20th yang 100%). Jupiter→Sagittarius: 3/4 naik (75%), termasuk +8,1% di Des 1982. Jupiter→Pisces: 5/7 naik (71%). Kesimpulan: domisili Saturn &amp; Jupiter tetap condong bullish walau diperluas ke 50 tahun, tapi Saturn→Capricorn spesifik lebih lemah dari yang dikira.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="sun-leo">
          <div class="section-head"><span class="num">05</span><h2>History Sun → Leo vs Gold (1975–2025)</h2><span class="sub">50 TAHUN · 51 KEJADIAN · JENDELA -5D/+7D</span></div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-dim);margin:-6px 0 14px">Sun ingress ke Leo terjadi tiap tahun (annual, presisi ~22-24 Jul). 51 kejadian penuh sejak data floating-price Gold tersedia (1975).</p>
          <div class="stat-row" style="margin-bottom:16px">
            <div class="stat"><b>37/51</b>tahun naik (73%)</div>
            <div class="stat"><b>+1,41%</b>rata-rata perubahan</div>
            <div class="stat"><b>+12,8%</b>terkuat (1978)</div>
            <div class="stat"><b>−4,8%</b>terlemah (2008)</div>
          </div>
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th colspan="4">5 KEJADIAN PALING BULLISH</th></tr><tr><th>Tahun</th><th>Sebelum</th><th>Sesudah</th><th>Perubahan</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>1978</td><td>186,0</td><td>209,8</td><td style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:700">+12,8% ⬆⬆</td></tr>
              <tr><td>2020</td><td>1.810,0</td><td>1.966,8</td><td style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:700">+8,7% ⬆⬆</td></tr>
              <tr><td>1987</td><td>449,3</td><td>475,1</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+5,7% ⬆</td></tr>
              <tr><td>1975</td><td>165,4</td><td>173,8</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+5,1% ⬆</td></tr>
              <tr><td>1993</td><td>392,9</td><td>411,3</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+4,7% ⬆</td></tr>
            </tbody>
            <thead><tr><th colspan="4">5 KEJADIAN PALING BEARISH</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>2008</td><td>958,0</td><td>912,3</td><td style="color:var(--mars);font-weight:700">−4,8% ⬇</td></tr>
              <tr><td>2002</td><td>317,1</td><td>306,0</td><td style="color:var(--mars)">−3,5% ⬇</td></tr>
              <tr><td>2015</td><td>1.131,9</td><td>1.095,1</td><td style="color:var(--mars)">−3,3% ⬇</td></tr>
              <tr><td>2004</td><td>406,8</td><td>393,7</td><td style="color:var(--mars)">−3,2% ⬇</td></tr>
              <tr><td>1976</td><td>117,9</td><td>114,2</td><td style="color:var(--mars)">−3,1% ⬇</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px"><h3>Temuan (51 kejadian, 50 tahun)</h3><p><b>73% naik</b> — ini window terpanjang &amp; paling stabil hasilnya (mirip 20th=65% &amp; 10th=80%, semua condong bullish, cuma beda magnitude konsistensi). Kejadian paling ekstrem (1978 +12,8%) terjadi di era gold bull-run akhir 1970an. Kesimpulan final: Sun→Leo adalah pola musiman PALING RELIABLE di seluruh dashboard ini — bullish di 3 window berbeda (10/20/50 tahun) dengan rentang 65-80%.</p></div>
        </section>

        <section id="venus-taurus">
          <div class="section-head"><span class="num">06</span><h2>History Venus → Taurus vs Gold — 50 Tahun</h2><span class="sub">DATA ASLI · GCUSD · 52 KEJADIAN</span></div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-dim);margin:-6px 0 14px">Venus ingress tiap tahun tapi tanggalnya geser jauh krn siklus ~225 hari + retrograde. Window: 5 hari sebelum vs 14 hari sesudah.</p>
          <div class="stat-row" style="margin-bottom:16px">
            <div class="stat"><b>21/52</b>naik (40%)</div>
            <div class="stat"><b>−0,50%</b>rata-rata perubahan</div>
            <div class="stat"><b>+10,8%</b>terkuat (1979)</div>
            <div class="stat"><b>−12,6%</b>terlemah (2006)</div>
          </div>
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th colspan="4">5 KEJADIAN PALING BULLISH</th></tr><tr><th>Tahun</th><th>Sebelum</th><th>Sesudah</th><th>Perubahan</th></tr></thead>
